<layout title="About">
  <:heading><h1>About</h1></:heading>
  <p>A small demo of <code>can</code> wired up to a Kemal server.</p>
  <p>
    The <code>layout</code> component lives in <code>layout.can</code> and is
    loaded at class scope so it can take slots. Each page <code>.can</code>
    file is loaded inside its handler method, where its content is rendered
    inside the layout via slot fills.
  </p>
</layout>
